Patch Set 3: Code-Review-1

Thanks Brian, this is great to see.

I think it would be great to clarify which (if any) 'officially defined' tasks a user should expect to see.

For example, devstack seems to support 'image_import' [1].

Is that just an example what can be done with tasks or is it something that users should expect to see and operators should be expected to support?

[1] http://paste.openstack.org/show/462919
